4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field and aims to help them start a career as data scientists and build their first ML models. The course highlights that graduates will be ready to enter tech's highest-paying fields in just 16 weeks. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. It covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course also provides opportunities to practice solving real-life cases and develop AI projects. It has a duration of 16 weeks with 3 classes weekly, and the class size is limited to 12 people. The course is available in English and Spanish. Upon completion, students receive recognized certificates. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop